e:T797,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Article Forge better than Longshot AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Article Forge scores 4.0 overall while Longshot AI scores 6.0. Article Forge is best for bulk article generation and PBN content, while Longshot AI excels for fact-checked content and SEO articles."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Article Forge or Longshot AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Article Forge starts at $27/mo and Longshot AI starts at $19/mo.  Longshot AI offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Article Forge to Longshot AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Article Forge and Longshot AI support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Article Forge vs Longshot AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Article Forge holds an overall rating of 4/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10. Longshot AI has an overall rating of 6/10 and ease of use score of 7/10. Users praise Article Forge for fully automated one-click article generation and Longshot AI for unique fact-checking and citation features."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Article Forge or Longshot AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Longshot AI for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Article Forge remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize fully automated one-click article generation. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json