13:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Article Forge and Longshot AI share a solid foundation of core features including Long Form, Seo Tools. Where Article Forge pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Multilingual and Api Access, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Longshot AI uniquely offers Short Form and Templates and Tone Control and Plagiarism Check and Team Collaboration, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Article Forge holds an overall score of 4/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Longshot AI scores 6/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
14:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Longshot AI comes in at a lower starting price of $19/mo, while Article Forge begins at $27/mo. Longshot AI stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Article Forge requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
